00:54:38,770 --> 00:54:41,060
有后现代主义的风格
Heavy Metal meets House and Garden.

576
00:54:42,840 --> 00:54:43,910
太美了
Beautiful.

577
00:54:44,150 --> 00:54:49,270
一边是黑暗  野蛮  颓废
It's so dark and Gothic and... disgustingly decadent.

578
00:54:50,920 --> 00:54:53,910
一边却如此明亮  活泼
Yet so bright and chipper and...

579
00:54:55,220 --> 00:54:56,500
优雅保守
...conservative.

580
00:55:00,760 --> 00:55:03,370
正是你的个性
It's so you!

581
00:55:03,370 --> 00:55:05,690
完完全全的你
And yet, so you!

582
00:55:07,400 --> 00:55:10,840
很少人能像你一样完美地
Very few people are both a summer and a winter, but...

583
00:55:10,840 --> 00:55:14,550
融合了两种极端的品味
...but you pull it off nicely.

584
00:55:16,550 --> 00:55:18,100
讲重点
What's the point?

585
00:55:19,120 --> 00:55:20,620
有没有人告诉你
Has anyone ever told you

586
00:55:20,620 --> 00:55:24,020
你有严重的乱抓狂毛病
you have a serious impulse-control problem?!

587
00:55:25,290 --> 00:55:28,280
这就是重点
This is the point.

588
00:55:40,140 --> 00:55:44,240
我来示范我是如何找到你的
This is how I found you. Let me demonstrate.

589
00:55:50,150 --> 00:55:51,740
这是你的脑
This is your brain on the Box.

590
00:55:52,580 --> 00:55:54,530
这是小弟我的脑
This is my brain.

591
00:55:54,620 --> 00:55:57,050
有没有人还要玩吗?
Does anyone else feel like a fried egg?

592
00:55:57,190 --> 00:55:58,680
我还要再玩
I'll have more.

593
00:55:59,120 --> 00:56:02,010
没问题  不过要收费
There's more. But only the first one's free.

594
00:56:03,190 --> 00:56:04,930
我们来谈条件
Here's the bargain:

595
00:56:04,930 --> 00:56:07,670
你帮我找资金来生产这机器
You'll help me steal production capital...

596
00:56:07,670 --> 00:56:10,800
我让城市每部电视都装上它
...so I can put a Box on every TV in town...

597
00:56:10,800 --> 00:56:16,010
我就成了高谭市最聪明的生物
...and become Gotham's cleverest carbon-based life form!

598
00:56:16,010 --> 00:56:19,270
为了报答你们...
And in return....

599
00:56:19,410 --> 00:56:22,210
你们有听好吗?
Is everybody paying attention?

600
00:56:22,210 --> 00:56:25,120
我会帮你解出世纪之谜
I will help you solve the greatest riddle of all.

601
00:56:25,120 --> 00:56:27,230
有史以来最大的谜
The mother of all riddles:

602
00:56:28,560 --> 00:56:32,070
蝙蝠侠是何方神圣
Who is... Batman?

603
00:56:33,860 --> 00:56:36,200
你擅闯我秘密基地
You broke into our hideout.

604
00:56:36,200 --> 00:56:38,870
破坏这块净土的圣洁
You violated the sanctity of our lair.

605
00:56:38,870 --> 00:56:41,700
本该把你碎尸万段
We should crush your bones into powder.

606
00:56:41,700 --> 00:56:43,970
不过看在你点子不错的份上
But you pose an interesting proposition.

607
00:56:43,970 --> 00:56:46,310
丢铜板决定  大头朝上放了你
Therefore, heads, we accept,

608
00:56:46,310 --> 00:56:48,130
字朝上你就认命受死吧
and tails, we blow your damn head off.

609
00:57:04,130 --> 00:57:05,860
这一颗不错
Here's a good one.

610
00:57:05,960 --> 00:57:07,620
不对不对
No, no, no!

611
00:57:07,830 --> 00:57:09,770
这一颗更好
There is a good one.

612
00:57:11,400 --> 00:57:13,730
放着就好  我来晾
Leave that. I'll attend to it.

613
00:57:13,800 --> 00:57:15,990
我可不习惯被人伺候
I'm not used to being waited on.

614
00:57:40,930 --> 00:57:42,130
不要开枪
Don't shoot me!

615
00:57:42,130 --> 00:57:44,940
发什么楞  拿来
Don't eyeball me! Give me that!

616
00:57:48,140 --> 00:57:50,870
双面人  教我怎么揍人
Two-Face, show me how to punch a guy!

617
00:57:50,870 --> 00:57:54,040
简单得很  握拳  往后拉
It's dead simple, my boy. Ball up your fist, reach back...

618
00:57:54,040 --> 00:57:55,600
再用力打出去
...and assert yourself.

619
00:57:57,350 --> 00:57:59,460
有意思  我试试
That looks fun. Let me try.

620
00:58:00,350 --> 00:58:03,930
握拳  往后拉  用力打出去
Ball up the fist, reach way back ...assert yourself.

621
00:58:08,530 --> 00:58:11,300
十万零两百二十
One hundred thousand, two hundred and twenty.

622
00:58:11,930 --> 00:58:13,980
十万零...
One hundred and....

623
00:58:14,070 --> 00:58:15,380
又数乱了
I lost count!

624
00:58:17,240 --> 00:58:21,640
昨夜绿衣抢匪再度犯案
Last night another robbery, perpetrated by the green-suited menace...

625
00:58:21,640 --> 00:58:23,740
数百万元钻石遭窃
...resulting in millions in diamonds stolen,

626
00:58:23,740 --> 00:58:25,580
蝙蝠侠并未出现
with no sign of Batman.

627
00:58:25,580 --> 00:58:30,220
匪徒作案习惯在现场留下谜语
This new criminal's pattern of marking his crimes with puzzles...

628
00:58:30,220 --> 00:58:33,490
市井间以"谜天大圣"称呼之
...has Gothamites calling him The Riddler.

629
00:58:33,490 --> 00:58:37,120
显然他是你和蝙蝠侠的公敌
Apparently, you and Batman have a common enemy.

630
00:58:37,120 --> 00:58:39,700
这是一早送来的新谜语
That was with the morning mail.

631
00:58:41,430 --> 00:58:43,800
八条好汉勇往直前
"The eight of us go forth, not back,

632
00:58:43,800 --> 00:58:45,100
不回头
to protect our king...

633
00:58:45,100 --> 00:58:47,040
一心护主公
"...from attack."

634
00:58:47,150 --> 00:58:48,260
西洋棋的卒子
Chess pawns.

635
00:58:48,370 --> 00:58:49,540
时钟
Clock.

636
00:58:49,540 --> 00:58:50,470
火柴
Matches.

637
00:58:50,470 --> 00:58:52,270
都是人造的物件
All man-made objects.

638
00:58:52,510 --> 00:58:54,720
体积小  重量轻
Small in size, light in weight.

639
00:58:54,910 --> 00:58:56,460
之间有何关联?
What's the connection?

640
00:58:56,610 --> 00:59:00,320
这就是他外号谜天大圣的原因
With all due respect, that's why they call him The Riddler.

641
00:59:03,020 --> 00:59:04,850
有事要我效劳吗?
May I help you?

642
00:59:04,850 --> 00:59:07,490
为什么只有这门上了锁?
Why is this the only locked door?

643
00:59:07,490 --> 00:59:09,320
门后是什么?
What's back there?

644
00:59:09,320 --> 00:59:12,380
主人韦恩死去的太太
Master Wayne's dead wives.

645
00:59:12,660 --> 00:59:15,400
那是放银器的柜子
The silver closet. On your way.

646
00:59:18,500 --> 00:59:22,070
现在各位可以体验伟大的科技
Now, you can be part of the action!

647
00:59:22,070 --> 00:59:24,470
尼格玛科技集团让您在家中
Nygma Tech brings the joy of 3-D

648
00:59:24,470 --> 00:59:26,730
享受3D立体声光娱乐
entertainment into your home!

649
00:59:27,440 --> 00:59:32,520
各位  我们的理想
Ladies and gentlemen, let me tell you... my vision.

650
00:59:33,820 --> 00:59:36,790
这魔幻宝盒享誉全美
The Box in every home in America...

651
00:59:36,790 --> 00:59:39,110
即将风行全世界
...and one day, the world!

652
00:59:39,250 --> 00:59:42,290
本地消息  艾德华的魔幻宝盒
In local news, Edward Nygma's 3-D Box...

653
00:59:42,290 --> 00:59:44,960
已在本市掀起购买热潮
...has become the rage of Gotham.

654
00:59:44,960 --> 00:59:49,630
昨晚所有家电行被抢购一空
Rioting occurred last night at electronic stores that were sold out.

655
00:59:49,630 --> 00:59:53,110
几乎全市每户皆有安装
There is hardly a home without the Nygma Tech Box.

656
00:59:53,540 --> 00:59:57,010
评论家认为这是机械化的沉沦
Critics claim the Box turns Gothamites into zombies.

657
00:59:57,010 --> 00:59:59,010
但艾德华本人有不同看法
But Edward Nygma just shrugs.

658
00:59:59,010 --> 01:00:01,820
电视发明时  他们也是这么说
"That's what they said when TV was invented."

659
01:00:44,660 --> 01:00:46,390
小主人
Master Dick!

660
01:00:47,830 --> 01:00:49,380
在这儿
Up here.

661
01:00:50,030 --> 01:00:52,910
没什么事  小主人
Just checking, young sir.

662
01:01:21,170 --> 01:01:26,400
遭非法闯入  注意!
Intruder alert. Intruder alert.

663
01:01:51,890 --> 01:01:55,260
我有东西给你  在桌上
I have something for you. It's on the table.

664
01:01:55,260 --> 01:01:57,480
希望你会喜欢
I hope you like it.

665
01:02:07,840 --> 01:02:10,950
这是出于专业上的直觉
Call it clinical intuition.

666
01:02:10,950 --> 01:02:14,140
你的梦境需要改变一下
l thought your dreams needed changing.

667
01:02:16,250 --> 01:02:19,360
我父母在我眼前遭人杀害
My parents were murdered before me...

668
01:02:19,360 --> 01:02:21,930
当时我只是个孩子
...when I was a kid.

669
01:02:23,860 --> 01:02:28,670
详细经过我记不太清楚
I don't... remember a lot of what happened, but...

670
01:02:28,670 --> 01:02:33,900
但在梦境中却历历在目
...what I do comes to me in my dreams. Flashes.

671
01:02:34,270 --> 01:02:38,280
最近梦中却出现一些新的内容
There's a new element now though, I haven't seen before.

672
01:02:38,280 --> 01:02:41,500
是一本红皮册子
It's a red leather book.

673
01:02:41,780 --> 01:02:44,140
新的梦境
Something else....

674
01:02:44,480 --> 01:02:48,120
甚至连我醒时都常会作这些梦
My dreams come to me when I'm awake now.

675
01:02:48,120 --> 01:02:51,590
布鲁斯  这是你压抑下的记忆
Bruce, you're describing repressed memories.

676
01:02:51,590 --> 01:02:57,750
记忆深处的痛苦会试着被释放
lmages of a forgotten pain that's trying to surface.

677
01:02:58,960 --> 01:03:00,210
我马上回来
I'll be right back.

678
01:03:13,480 --> 01:03:16,950
蝙蝠侠法外锄奸令人争议

679
01:03:20,090 --> 01:03:22,220
精神分裂诊断书
Is there an aspect of your

680
01:03:22,220 --> 01:03:23,880
关于你父母之死
parents' death you haven't faced?

681
01:03:23,890 --> 01:03:25,860
是否有什么你不敢面对的
You were so young

682
01:03:25,860 --> 01:03:28,010
当时你还很小
when it happened.

683
01:03:28,290 --> 01:03:31,940
也许我该让你专心研究蝙蝠侠
Maybe I should leave you two alone.

684
01:03:32,030 --> 01:03:36,520
这该不会只是把公事带回家吧
This goes way beyond taking your work home, doesn't it?

685
01:03:38,570 --> 01:03:39,960
好吧
All right.

686
01:03:41,940 --> 01:03:43,990
我承认他够刺激
I think he's fascinating.

687
01:03:44,310 --> 01:03:46,080
心理学角度上的
Clinically.

688
01:03:46,080 --> 01:03:48,440
为什么一个男人会这么做?
Why does a man do this?

689
01:03:48,920 --> 01:03:51,190
仿佛受到诅咒般在赎罪
It's as if he's cursed to pay penance.

690
01:03:51,190 --> 01:03:53,250
他到底犯了什么错
What crime could he have committed to

691
01:03:53,250 --> 01:03:57,160
注定要在夜间出没受惩罚
deserve a life of nightly torture?

692
01:03:57,160 --> 01:04:02,510
只是专业上的好奇吗? 慈丝?
It's more than just... professional interest, isn't it, Chase?

693
01:04:03,330 --> 01:04:05,380
你在吃醋吗?
Bruce, are you jealous?

694
01:04:05,930 --> 01:04:11,700
不  我无法吃蝙蝠侠的醋
No. I can't be jealous of Batman.

695
01:04:11,840 --> 01:04:16,320
我想亲近你  你却拒人千里
I want to be close, but you won't let me near.

696
01:04:16,510 --> 01:04:20,020
有什么不想让我知道的吗?
What are you protecting me from?

697
01:04:20,020 --> 01:04:22,450
想知道原因吗?
Do you want to know me?

698
01:04:22,450 --> 01:04:24,880
你知道我是谁吗?
Do you want to know who I am?

699
01:04:26,360 --> 01:04:30,980
我想我们都有两种面貌
I guess... we're all two people.

700
01:04:32,130 --> 01:04:36,700
外表所呈现的  和内心真实的自我
One daylight, and the one we keep in shadow.

701
01:04:36,700 --> 01:04:41,200
愤怒  暴力  激情
Rage... violence... passion.

702
01:04:45,640 --> 01:04:46,750
对不起
Excuse me.

703
01:04:48,710 --> 01:04:49,680
我正在忙
I'm busy.

704
01:04:49,680 --> 01:04:54,380
抱歉打扰你  小主人惹麻烦了
I'm sorry to bother you. I have some distressing news about Dick.

705
01:04:54,380 --> 01:04:55,990
他还好吧?
Is he okay?

706
01:04:55,990 --> 01:04:58,690
他出门了
I'm afraid Master Dick has gone traveling.

707
01:04:59,660 --> 01:05:01,160
离家出走吗?
He ran away?

708
01:05:01,160 --> 01:05:04,460
事实上  他把车开走了
Actually, he took the car.

709
01:05:04,460 --> 01:05:06,460
把积架开走吗?
He boosted the Jag?

710
01:05:06,460 --> 01:05:08,070
不是那部积架
Not the Jaguar.

711
01:05:08,070 --> 01:05:09,570
另一部车
The other car.

712
01:05:09,570 --> 01:05:10,900
班特利吗?
Bentley? No, sir.

713
01:05:10,900 --> 01:05:14,970
不  主人  是"另外"一部车
The other car.

714
01:05:45,040 --> 01:05:48,790
小妞们  要去兜兜风吗?
Go for a little ride in my love machine, babies?

715
01:05:53,550 --> 01:05:55,050
是蝙蝠侠
It's Batman!

716
01:05:55,050 --> 01:05:57,520
快开门  蝙蝠侠
Open up, Batman.

717
01:05:58,750 --> 01:06:00,820
等等  他不是蝙蝠侠
Wait! That's not Batman!

718
01:06:00,820 --> 01:06:02,390
你说什么?
What do you mean?

719
01:06:02,390 --> 01:06:04,780
他是蝙蝠弟弟
That's Batboy!

720
01:06:05,060 --> 01:06:07,080
不是蝙蝠侠本人嘛
It ain't the Bat!

721
01:06:29,750 --> 01:06:31,140
放了她
Let her go!

722
01:06:38,860 --> 01:06:41,130
你是什么东西?
Who the hell are you?

723
01:06:41,130 --> 01:06:43,380
在下蝙蝠侠
I'm Batman.

724
01:06:44,770 --> 01:06:48,100
我忘了穿蝙蝠装  不行吗?
I forgot my suit, all right?

725
01:07:26,950 --> 01:07:28,440
快走
Come on, run!

726
01:07:28,750 --> 01:07:31,660
蝙蝠侠不和女士吻别吗?
Doesn't Batman ever kiss the girl?

727
01:07:33,450 --> 01:07:34,480
走!
Go!

728
01:07:34,650 --> 01:07:36,650
谢了  你救了我
Thanks, you saved my life!

729
01:07:36,650 --> 01:07:40,720
看来我天生是当超级英雄的料
I could definitely get into this superhero gig.

730
01:08:03,350 --> 01:08:05,010
蝙蝠侠来了!
Batman!

731
01:08:18,400 --> 01:08:19,900
你可恶!
Bastard!

732
01:08:19,900 --> 01:08:21,900
我家人成了你的替死鬼
It should've been you!

733
01:08:21,900 --> 01:08:25,170
当时你向双面人承认是你
If you had told Two-Face who you were at the circus...

734
01:08:25,170 --> 01:08:28,200
他们就都不会死了
...they'd still be alive!

735
01:08:30,850 --> 01:08:33,810
若能以布鲁斯韦恩的命来交换
If Bruce Wayne could've given his life for your family

736
01:08:33,810 --> 01:08:35,200
他会乐意的
he would have.

737
01:08:40,890 --> 01:08:44,570
我现在一心只想杀双面人
All I can think about every day is getting Two-Face.

738
01:08:45,460 --> 01:08:47,860
他毁了我的一生
He took my whole life.

739
01:08:49,500 --> 01:08:51,600
今晚我在干架时
When I was out there tonight...

740
01:08:51,600 --> 01:08:54,240
都把对手当成是他
...I imagined it was him I was fighting...

741
01:08:54,240 --> 01:08:57,230
连我在捶你时也一样
...even when I was fighting you...

742
01:08:57,270 --> 01:09:00,230
浑然忘了肉体的痛苦
...and the pain went away.

743
01:09:00,280 --> 01:09:01,970
你了解吗?
Do you understand?

744
01:09:01,980 --> 01:09:03,640
我了解
Yes, I do.

745
01:09:03,650 --> 01:09:07,750
很好  你一定得帮我找到他
Good. You must help me find him.

746
01:09:07,940 --> 01:09:08,940
那以后
When we do...

747
01:09:09,420 --> 01:09:11,820
我要亲手宰了他
...I'm the one who kills him.

748
01:09:13,260 --> 01:09:16,530
这是你一生的目标吗?
So, you're willing to take a life?

749
01:09:16,530 --> 01:09:19,790
是的  亲手杀了双面人
As long as it's Two-Face.

750
01:09:21,060 --> 01:09:24,740
然后事情就像这样
Then it will happen this way:

751
01:09:24,770 --> 01:09:30,970
你杀了双面人  痛苦却未远离
you make the kill. And your pain doesn't die with Harvey, it grows.

752
01:09:30,970 --> 01:09:33,550
反而与日俱增
So you run into the night to find another face, and another...

753
01:09:34,010 --> 01:09:37,880
夜复一夜  你不断借杀伐解脱
...and another...

754
01:09:37,880 --> 01:09:40,250
直到有一天你醒来
...until one terrible morning you wake up and realize...

755
01:09:40,250 --> 01:09:44,390
你将发现复仇成了生命的全部
...that revenge has become your whole life...

756
01:09:44,390 --> 01:09:47,490
而你却无法自拔
...and you won't know why.

757
01:09:47,490 --> 01:09:49,530
你不了解
You can't understand.

758
01:09:49,530 --> 01:09:53,400
你家人又没有被疯子杀掉
Your family wasn't killed by a maniac.

759
01:09:53,400 --> 01:09:56,230
他们就是这么死的
Yes, they were.

760
01:09:56,230 --> 01:09:58,100
我们同痛相怜
We're the same.

761
01:09:58,100 --> 01:10:00,340
