好
Clever.

815
01:14:09,800 --> 01:14:10,830
谢谢
Thanks.

816
01:14:10,830 --> 01:14:12,220
不客气
My pleasure.

817
01:14:41,700 --> 01:14:44,240
晚安  韦恩先生
Good evening, Mr. Wayne.

818
01:14:45,240 --> 01:14:52,100
