Whenever you go out at night, I'll be watching.

866
01:20:53,720 --> 01:20:56,630
蝙蝠侠去哪儿  我也跟着去
Where Batman goes, I'll go.

867
01:20:56,630 --> 01:20:59,300
你如何阻止我
How will you stop me?

868
01:20:59,300 --> 01:21:01,060
