No, you must let this go.

919
01:25:52,770 --> 01:25:54,570
听我的话  我是你朋友
Listen to me, I'm your friend.

920
01:25:54,570 --> 01:25:57,240
我不需要朋友  我要一个拍档
I don't need a friend, I need a partner.

921
01:25:57,240 --> 01:26:00,280
双面人要付出代价
Two-Face has got to pay.

922
01:26:00,280 --> 01:26:01,940
求求你
Please.

923
01:26:03,550 --> 01:26:05,920
慈丝来吃晚饭
Chase is coming for dinner. I'm going to tell her...

924
01:26:05,920 --> 01:26:09,190
