Which one will it be, Batman?

1144
01:49:58,180 --> 01:49:59,720
布鲁斯的最爱?
Bruce's love?

1145
01:49:59,720 --> 01:50:03,050
还是你的菜鸟拍档?
Or the Dark Knight's junior partner?

1146
