Wait! I have a riddle.

1152
01:50:22,440 --> 01:50:27,130
让我猜吗? 真的?
For me? Really?

1153
01:50:29,850 --> 01:50:31,270
快告诉我
Tell me.

1154
01:50:34,860 --> 01:50:37,290
有眼睛却看不到
I see without seeing.

1155
01:50:37,290 --> 01:50:41,150
黑夜如同白昼般清晰
To me, darkness is as clear as daylight.

1156
