Aren't you forgetting something?

1166
01:52:59,610 --> 01:53:01,480
你的铜板
Your coin.

1167
01:53:02,610 --> 01:53:05,350
你老是下不了决定
You're always of two minds.

1168
01:53:06,050 --> 01:53:08,370
没错  你说得对
Yes, of course. You're right.

1169
01:53:08,550 --> 01:53:11,550
人常为情绪左右而无法自制
Emotion's always the enemy of justice.

1170
01:53:11,550 --> 01:53:13,660
你真是我的哥儿们
You've always been a good friend.

1171
01:54:00,270 --> 01:54:02,040
为什么?
Why?

1172
01:54:02,440 --> 01:54:06,670
