Too many questions.

1174
01:54:11,680 --> 01:54:13,490
轩然大波
Too many questions.

1175
01:54:13,780 --> 01:54:15,520
可怜的家伙
Poor Edward.

1176
01:54:15,650 --> 01:54:17,980
我一定得救两个
I had to save them both.

1177
01:54:18,190 --> 01:54:21,590
布鲁斯韦恩就是蝙蝠侠
You see, I'm both Bruce Wayne and Batman.

1178
01:54:21,590 --> 01:54:23,590
这不只是我的义务
Not because I have to be.

1179
01:54:23,590 --> 01:54:28,010
也是我选择的生活方式
Now... because I choose to be.

1180
01:54:46,520 --> 01:54:49,060
阿甘精神病院

1181
01:54:51,020 --> 01:54:54,390
