Thank you for responding to my request for a consultation, Dr. Meridian.

1182
01:54:55,590 --> 01:54:56,840
艾德华尼格玛一直鬼叫鬼喊
Edward Nygma...

1183
01:54:56,840 --> 01:55:02,430
宣称他知道蝙蝠侠的真实身份
...has been screaming for hours that he knows the true identity... of Batman.

1184
01:55:16,280 --> 01:55:17,780
艾德华
Edward?

1185
01:55:18,420 --> 01:55:21,180
是谁呀?
Who... is it?

1186
01:55:23,960 --> 01:55:27,110
我是梅慈丝医生
It's Dr. Meridian. Chase.

1187
01:55:27,630 --> 01:55:29,710
记得我吗?
Do you remember me?

1188
01:55:31,770 --> 01:55:34,160
怎么忘得了呢?
How could I forget?

1189
01:55:34,800 --> 01:55:37,470
波顿医生告诉我...
Dr. Burton tells me...

1190
01:55:37,840 --> 01:55:40,790
你知道谁是蝙蝠侠
...you know who Batman is.

1191
01:55:40,980 --> 01:55:45,140
你不说"请"我就不告诉你
I can't tell you if you don't say, "please."

1192
01:55:45,210 --> 01:55:47,540
艾德华  请问你
Edward, please.

1193
01:55:47,620 --> 01:55:50,460
谁是蝙蝠侠
Who is Batman?

1194
01:55:51,590 --> 01:55:54,480
就...是...我
I'm... Batman.

1195
01:56:20,480 --> 01:56:22,920
你的秘密安全得很
Your secret is safe.

1196
01:56:22,920 --> 01:56:25,890
他百分之百是个狂人
He is definitely a wacko.

1197
01:56:25,890 --> 01:56:27,420
狂人
Wacko.

1198
01:56:27,420 --> 01:56:31,140
这是心理学专有名词吗?
Is that a technical term? Listen...

1199
01:56:34,430 --> 01:56:37,690
我想我不需要这个了
...I won't need this anymore.

1200
01:56:39,900 --> 01:56:44,070
